<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title></title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="row align-center">
        <div class="small-12 large-8 medium-8 ">
        <%= link_to "&larr; New Search".html_safe, patients_path, class: "button margin-bottom-10"  %>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row align-center">
        <div class="card columns small-12 large-8 medium-8 patient-info">
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Name</th>
                        <th>Patient #</th>
                        <th>Date of Birth</th>
                        <th>Age</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td><%= @patient.first_name%> <%= @patient.last_name %></td>
                        <td><%= @patient.patient_number %></td>
                        <td><%= @patient.dob.strftime("%m/%d/%Y")%></td>
                        <td><%= @patient.age%></td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row align-center">
        <div class="card columns small-8" id="callout-patient">
            <%if @patient.patient_number < 5 %>
            <div class="callout success">
                <svg width="70" height="70" viewBox="0 0 1792 1792" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M1412 734q0-28-18-46l-91-90q-19-19-45-19t-45 19l-408 407-226-226q-19-19-45-19t-45 19l-91 90q-18 18-18 46 0 27 18 45l362 362q19 19 45 19 27 0 46-19l543-543q18-18 18-45zm252 162q0 209-103 385.5t-279.5 279.5-385.5 103-385.5-103-279.5-279.5-103-385.5 103-385.5 279.5-279.5 385.5-103 385.5 103 279.5 279.5 103 385.5z" fill="#fff"/></svg>
                <h3>Up To Date</h3>
                <p>The patient is up to date. <!-- Next vaccine due: VAX on
                DATE. --></p>
            </div><%elsif @patient.patient_number < 10 %>
            <div class="callout warning">
                <svg height="70" viewbox="0 0 1792 1792" width="70" xmlns=
                "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d=
                "M1024 1376v-192q0-14-9-23t-23-9h-192q-14 0-23 9t-9 23v192q0 14 9 23t23 9h192q14 0 23-9t9-23zm256-672q0-88-55.5-163t-138.5-116-170-41q-243 0-371 213-15 24 8 42l132 100q7 6 19 6 16 0 25-12 53-68 86-92 34-24 86-24 48 0 85.5 26t37.5 59q0 38-20 61t-68 45q-63 28-115.5 86.5t-52.5 125.5v36q0 14 9 23t23 9h192q14 0 23-9t9-23q0-19 21.5-49.5t54.5-49.5q32-18 49-28.5t46-35 44.5-48 28-60.5 12.5-81zm384 192q0 209-103 385.5t-279.5 279.5-385.5 103-385.5-103-279.5-279.5-103-385.5 103-385.5 279.5-279.5 385.5-103 385.5 103 279.5 279.5 103 385.5z"
                fill="#000"></path></svg>
                <div class="explanation">
                    <h2>Review Needed</h2>
                    <p>Please have a nurse review the record.</p><!--<ul>
                        <li><strong>Invalid vaccine:</strong> the VAX
                        dose given on DATE was not valid, because it was given
                        X days after the first dose. These doses must be given
                        at least X days apart.</li>
                        <li><strong>Past due vaccine:</strong> X dose of
                        VAX, due by DATE is missing.</li>
                    </ul>-->
                </div>
            </div><%else %>
            <div class="callout alert">
                <svg height="70" viewbox="0 0 1792 1792" width="70" xmlns=
                "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d=
                "M896 128q209 0 385.5 103t279.5 279.5 103 385.5-103 385.5-279.5 279.5-385.5 103-385.5-103-279.5-279.5-103-385.5 103-385.5 279.5-279.5 385.5-103zm128 1247v-190q0-14-9-23.5t-22-9.5h-192q-13 0-23 10t-10 23v190q0 13 10 23t23 10h192q13 0 22-9.5t9-23.5zm-2-344l18-621q0-12-10-18-10-8-24-8h-220q-14 0-24 8-10 6-10 18l17 621q0 10 10 17.5t24 7.5h185q14 0 23.5-7.5t10.5-17.5z"
                fill="#fff"></path></svg>
                <div class="explanation">
                    <h2>Vaccine Due</h2>
                    <p>The patient requires additional vaccines.</p>
                    <!--<ul>
                        <li><strong>Invalid vaccine:</strong> the VAX
                        dose given on DATE was not valid, because it was given
                        X days after the first dose. These doses must be given
                        at least X days apart.</li>
                        <li><strong>Past due vaccine:</strong> X dose of
                        VAX, due by DATE is missing.</li>
                    </ul>-->
                </div>
            </div><%end %>
        </div>
    </div><!-- temp for demo -->
    <%= render 'all_vaccine_groups', view_patient: @patient%>
</body>
</html>